<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7778c0ad-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s410nnn–6"><num value="410nnn–6">§ 410nnn–6.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is authorized to be appropriated $6,000,000 for acquisition of lands and interests in lands for purposes of the Palo Alto Battlefield National Historical Park.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7778c0ae-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/102/304/s8">Pub. L. 102–304, § 8</ref>, <date date="1992-06-23">June 23, 1992</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/106/258">106 Stat. 258</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/111/11/tVII/s7113/a/3/A">Pub. L. 111–11, title VII, § 7113(a)(3)(A)</ref>, <date date="2009-03-30">Mar. 30, 2009</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/123/1201">123 Stat. 1201</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
