<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id7778c0b1-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2009—<ref href="/us/pl/111/11">Pub. L. 111–11</ref> substituted “National Historical Park” for “National Historic Site”.</p>
